47
00:09:19,563 --> 00:09:21,986
Clark, thank you for coming.

48
00:09:22,081 --> 00:09:23,838
It's good to see you.

49
00:09:38,617 --> 00:09:42,854
How's Lex? I've been trying to contact him
since I heard, but he won't speak to me.

50
00:09:42,933 --> 00:09:45,272
He thinks you're trying to frame him.

51
00:09:46,476 --> 00:09:47,867
Are you?

52
00:09:49,804 --> 00:09:52,861
- No Clark.
- Why should I believe you?

53
00:09:52,895 --> 00:09:55,966
There's no reason you should.

54
00:09:57,157 --> 00:10:01,594
Listen to me, I was ill, Clark...

55
00:10:01,656 --> 00:10:06,327
The liver disease I had was
a death sentence...

56
00:10:06,821 --> 00:10:11,352
and something happened, I can't
explain it...

57
00:10:11,384 --> 00:10:16,352
I woke up on the floor, there
was a riot... I

58
00:10:18,508 --> 00:10:21,856
I felt as if...

59
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:27,923
a different kind of energy had been..
inside me,

60
00:10:27,952 --> 00:10:35,152
something strong, and...
good.

61
00:10:36,767 --> 00:10:40,330
I was changed.

62
00:10:40,864 --> 00:10:44,629
And my liver had healed!

63
