night, I can't seem to shake it.

86
00:12:42,541 --> 00:12:45,669
Oh, I'm sorry, Lana.
You have a visitor.

87
00:12:48,730 --> 00:12:51,496
She's here for me?
Thanks.

88
00:12:56,327 --> 00:12:58,322
Excuse me.

89
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:01,528
Lana!

90
00:13:01,866 --> 00:13:07,437
It's wonderful to finally meet you.
You are beautiful.

91
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:10,629
I'm sorry, do I know you?

92
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:12,997
I'm Jason's mother.

93
00:13:14,374 --> 00:13:18,233
- Did I catch you off-guard?
- No... no.

94
00:13:18,714 --> 00:13:24,711
