- I've got to believe somebody, Chloe.

142
00:17:09,039 --> 00:17:10,859
There it is.

143
00:17:13,677 --> 00:17:18,524
Eve Andrews, Age 28.
Lives in Metropolis.

144
00:17:46,663 --> 00:17:47,797
Lex.

145
00:17:48,519 --> 00:17:51,551
- What are you doing?
- I'm saving my ass, Clark.

146
00:17:51,629 --> 00:17:54,458
What the hell are you doing here?

147
00:17:57,921 --> 00:18:00,687
You've got to help me... Please.

148
00:18:09,043 --> 00:18:12,971
You were burning evidence, Lex.
Not exactly the actions of an innocent man!

149
00:18:13,056 --> 00:18:15,400
Come on, Clark, think about it!

150
00:18:15,464 --> 00:18:18,711
If I killed that girl, Why would I take a nap
next to her body so the maid can find me?

151
00:18:18,770 --> 00:18:21,907
- It doesn't make any sense.
-Nor does breaking into her house, but you did that.

152
00:18:23,945 --> 00:18:26,541
You better be honest with me, cause
right now, I'm an accomplice.

153
00:18:26,551 --> 00:18:28,839
I didn't ask you to show up.

154
00:18:29,062 --> 00:18:31,197
